      "udl_alignment_cast_guidelines": "🎨 ການຈັດແນວ UDL — ຄຳແນະນຳ CAST",
      "every_fraction_lab_feature_mapped_to_a": "ທຸກຄຸນສົມບັດ Fraction Lab ຖືກຈັບຄູ່ກັບຄຳແນະນຳ Universal Design for Learning (UDL) ຈາກ CAST ",
